      "created": "2016-04-12T18:52:13.928+0000",
      "description": "The initial configuration approach for the DNS service specified a bind-address that designated the network interface to which the service should bind its listener port.  However, there is a need to potentially specify multiple DNS service instances (HA approach) and therefore a need to specify bind addresses for each instance (and those interfaces may vary between hosts).  This may take a for similar to the RM HA approach (rm1, rm2)",
